<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>You're subscribed to Plenty Value Newsletter</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Segoe UI, Arial, sans-serif; background: #f5f5f5; margin: 0; padding: 20px; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: white; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
    .header { background: #001845; color: white; padding: 40px 20px; text-align: center; }
    .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 28px; }
    .tagline { font-size: 14px; margin-top: 10px; }
    .content { padding: 40px; color: #333; }
    .content p { margin: 0 0 20px 0; line-height: 1.6; }
    .content ul { padding-left: 20px; }
    .content li { margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .cta-button { display: inline-block; background: #81C14B; color: white; padding: 12px 30px; border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; margin: 20px 0; }
    .footer { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 20px; text-align: center; color: #666; font-size: 12px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Plenty Value</h1>
      <p class="tagline">Expert Product Reviews & Deals Newsletter</p>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Welcome, {{ name }}! 🎉</p>
      <p>You've been successfully subscribed to our newsletter. Here's what to expect:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>📱 Curated product reviews from industry experts</li>
        <li>💰 Exclusive deals and affiliate opportunities</li>
        <li>💡 Tips and insights for the latest products</li>
        <li>🎁 Early access to featured products</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Thank you for being part of the Plenty Value community!</p>
      <a href="{{ app_url }}/marketplace" class="cta-button">Browse Marketplace</a>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>To unsubscribe from these emails, click the unsubscribe link in any email.</p>
      <p>&copy; 2026 Plenty Value. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
